# duckdb-not-gt

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `duckdb_inspired_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (not (gt ?x ?y))
rhs: (le ?x ?y)
